sentences.english: Most customers are from Shanxi and Erduosi (Inner Momgolia).

sentences.english: Aim To study the secondary porosity in the clastic rock storage of Ordos Basin.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究鄂尔多斯盆地碎屑岩储集体中的次生孔隙。

sentences.english: The western margin of Ordos basin has experienced complicated tectonic evolution and the ordovician is the most important stages in its evolutive history.
sentences.chinese: 奥陶纪是鄂尔多斯西缘构造沉积演化的重要构成阶段。

sentences.english: Bottle turn the star moves, years alternate, old E Er is much this now is changed new colour.

sentences.english: The Ordos basin on late-Mesozoic exist on a tectonic heat event.
sentences.chinese: 鄂尔多斯盆地在中生代晚期存在一期构造热事件。

sentences.english: The main type of the west margin tectonics belt of the Ordos massif is characterised by thrust nappe.
sentences.chinese: 鄂尔多斯地块西缘构造带的主要形式是逆冲推覆构造。

sentences.english: The palaeogeomorphic form of the pre-Jurassic was reconstructed by the method of mold.
sentences.chinese: 应用印模法恢复了鄂尔多斯盆地前侏罗纪古地貌形态。

sentences.english: Youfangzhuang area lies in the west of Northern Shanxi Slope, Ordos Basin.
sentences.chinese: 油坊庄地区位于鄂尔多斯盆地陕北斜坡西部。

sentences.english: A deserted street in the Kangbashi district of the town of Ordos in China's Inner Mongolia Autonomous Region.
sentences.chinese: 中国内蒙古自治区鄂尔多斯康巴什区的一条废弃街道。

sentences.english: Ordos is the new face of coal in China.
sentences.chinese: 鄂尔多斯代表着中国煤矿工业的新面孔。

sentences.english: Zichang oilfield is located in the eastern slope of Ordos basin.
sentences.chinese: 子长油田位于鄂尔多斯盆地东部斜坡。

sentences.english: The Jingbian Gasfield is located in the central of the Ordos Basin.
sentences.chinese: 靖边气田位于鄂尔多斯盆地的中部地区。

sentences.english: Tabamiao area is situated in Yishan slope of Ordos Basin.
sentences.chinese: 塔巴庙地区区域构造上隶属于鄂尔多斯盆地伊陕斜坡。

sentences.english: CTCC Round 4 will be held on 10th Jul, at Odors International Circuit, Neimenggu.
sentences.chinese: 第四分站将在鄂尔多斯国际赛车场举行。

sentences.english: Both trends are apparent at Ordos.
sentences.chinese: 两种趋势都在鄂尔多斯显而易见。
